      <methods>
         <methodStep>
            <description>
               <section>
                  <title>Experimental Design</title>
                  <para>Five 10 meter probe lines were established using fiberglass poles within this area.  At each site 10 poles were set at 1 meter intervals.  These sites include an unburned control (BFCONTROL), an unburned fireline (BFFIRELINEUNBURNED), an unburned safety zone (BFSAFETYZONE), a burned fireline (BFFIRELINEBURNED), and a burned are (BFBURN).  
</para>
               </section>
               <section>
                  <title>Methods</title>
                  <para>Thaw depth is measured in cm using a graduated frost probe. Measurements are done in mid to late September as close as possible to maximum thaw depth.
</para>
               </section>
            </description>
         </methodStep>
